{
  "chapter": 81,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十一回：七叶果。秦百龄向芮玮透露摄魂针的三种毒——摄魂针、追魂针、失魂针，各有不同控制效果。秦百龄告知如梦大师种有七叶果，其果可解摄魂针之毒，但如梦大师武功深不可测。秦百龄以此为条件，要求芮玮去铁网帮盗取月形门秘籍玄龟集，被芮玮拒绝。秦百龄带走芮玮儿子为人质。白燕的二姐桃根出现，因芮玮放走刘育芷坏了她的生意而要杀他。白燕及时赶到阻止，亮出芮玮是自己种影的身份。桃根透露姚济生买影子是为了强娶刘育芷。白燕给芮玮三日自由，芮玮决定闯慈悲庵盗七叶果解毒。深夜上山时，发现一黑影似是自己母亲。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她们是香神之后当然能避免那种臭味了，否则摄魂针不是做法自毙？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "至于香的原因我也不知，但是知道那迷人的香味，你闻多了，不爱的人也渐渐爱上，终至不可分离。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "果真如此我避免见她，不闻她身上香味怎会被迷！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "说的容易，你不见她成吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "买影人三种针任那一种皆令你此生不得自由，嘿！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "嘿！若不是知道买影人的厉害，我秦白龄不会前去求买影人吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "秦白龄老了无福消受摄魂针，至少还能受那两针。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你大概不知道追魂针的厉害，倘若买影人看不中你，认为你配不上她，种子不好，那时你求她卖影子只有受前两针了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "那两针又如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "追魂针一月发作一次，不服她买影人的解药，一月时间到魂归阴曹，想一月一月活下去，哼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "哼！那你只得月月替她买影人卖命了，她要你做什么事就不得推辞。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "至于失魂针更惨，中了此针变成白痴，这一生只认得她买影人一人，也就是买影人成了惟一主人，中针那人像条狗一样，主人要他咬谁就咬谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老弟，中那第三针，你算幸运的了，其实想开点，中了此针该庆幸呢，哈哈，老弟，将来你的种子开花，生了女儿就是未来的买影人，可是千万不要再生儿子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "老匹夫，你……你当日为何不明言三种针的厉害，怂恿我去求买影人，如今说不是迟了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老弟，你可别不识抬举，没有我的指点，你能做白燕的丈夫吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "什么狗屁丈夫，'有君子，失影人'这两句话我现在才了解，她无影门也太绝了，难道男人不是人，非要是她的奴才，处处听她吩咐？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "这样的丈夫谁想当！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有艳福可享管他那么多，老弟，你的丈夫气也太重了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "秦百龄，你再讽刺我，莫怪我芮玮将来对你不利！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "莫气，莫气，小老儿不敢再讽刺阁下，咱们谈正经的吧。现在补救还不迟。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "你说怎么还不迟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "亡羊补牢，末之晚也。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "怎么个不晚法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你当真舍不得种子外借？要知买影人选种，对方人品，外貌皆是上上之选，一经选中势难放手，你要考虑不做白燕丈夫其后果很严重呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "毫无考虑的余地，男女相配要双方两厢情愿，哪有任她女方做主的道理，再说我不希望将来的女儿做个于人无异的买影人！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，你既这样说，我就指一条名径。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "且慢，姓秦的，假若你想设计害我，只要我芮玮不死，誓不与你罢休。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这话说得难听了，你怕我害你，干脆别谈。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你相信我，咱们就谈，而且有条件呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "条件不慌，先说补救的方法，如梦大师，老弟，你一定认识她老人家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "当然认识，阁下的祖奶奶大大有名人物，晚辈岂有不识之理？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这还有假吗，天下有种七叶果你听说过没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "七叶果一叶大注七瓣，十载一开花，花呈淡红色，百年一结果，花果皆为不世药，尤其果子更为贵重，可惜一枝只能结果一次，结果后花凋叶残枯萎而死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "听那刘姑娘说你是药王爷弟子，果不愧圣手如来药王爷的名头，有其师必有其徒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "七叶果书上虽有记载，却道此果极难栽培，古来只有一人栽活过，但也只有栽成一枝，第二枝就栽不活了，难不成如梦大师也栽活一枝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "对呀！难怪如梦大师把七叶果供为奇宝，原因种活它有这等难处，呵呵，老弟，那果子你偷吃后，我那祖奶奶怕要活活气死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "你怎知如梦大师种的七叶果生出果子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不知道？跟你不等于说废话，要解摄魂针之毒惟有那果子吃下才成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "据我所知——其花亦能解天下各种迷药之毒……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "花，花有何用，我最近才知如梦大师的七叶果长了果子了，老弟，你要把握机会啊，机会一失不再来，别等果子落了，你这摄魂针之毒，一辈子也解不了，难道再栽一枝等百年后去吃果子，那时老弟……哼，咱们作古啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "只怕……只怕……如梦大师也要吃那果子，她辛苦种子百年我去拣个现成，怎么说都不对。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "人不为己，天诛地灭，老弟，你是怕捋虎须，如梦大师的武功，哼！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "哼！不是我说，小老弟，你差得太远了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "我虽知武功大不如她，你说得不错，为了自己，这虎须我倒要去捋捋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这才是男子汉大丈夫讲的话，老弟，斗智不斗力，老哥预祝你马到成功，再说素心那妮子，乘机会也好会会，是不？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "只是随那老古怪的如幻大师，看得紧，管得严，可不大方便，最好找个方便的地方，那时你老弟……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老弟，至于我的条件很简单，事成了麻烦你长江一行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "你要我去长江做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我的意图与刘姑娘那师父一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "怎么？你要我到铁网帮骗取月形门秘籍玄龟集！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不好意思，老哥只望你替我办妥这件事，不怕丢人，百年前的太阳门一直与月形门为敌，但总占不了上风，原因月形门武术不下太阳门，玄龟集是月形门的武术总鉴，本门曾派女弟子乔装至月形门卧底就是窃取那玄龟集，结果，咳，赔了夫人又折兵，现今太阳门再出，玄龟集不得，终无高枕之日。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "不行，不行，甭说我不屑为，有本领明枪明刀互斗，取对方秘术算哪门子英雄，秦先生，你身为太阳门再世的领导人物，要怕月形门与你为敌，该力研本门武功对抗，盗取玄龟集一事，芮某决不赞同。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我早算定你不会答应的，哼！哼……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你相好来了，老哥不便留，记住设法抛开她，据我所知，你离开她三天可忍，尽这三天时间速盗七叶果……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "text": "把我儿子留下。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_bai_ling",
      "speaker_name": "秦百龄",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你儿子留为人质，以玄龟集来换……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "喂，你姓什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我难看要你皱什么眉头，不想看把眼睛闭着。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘，慢来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到底是不是人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "我不是人，姑娘也不是人了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你敢骂人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "并非我骂人，姑娘在骂自己，咱们一样有鼻有眼，你说我不是人，岂不是在骂你自己不是人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要是人，人是合群的动物，怎么我要走过来都不准。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘过来对我不利，在下通情达理不愿起无谓争端，怎说不准你走来，只怕你要打我啊？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我与你无冤无仇，怎会平白打你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "再说我身上很臭，怕姑娘闻到不舒服，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，你不用多说啦，我不过来就是，我要问你句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘请问，在下洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你为何安葬这三人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "尸体入土为安，我不忍见他们横尸日光下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不信你有这好心。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "在下不敢以好心自居，只问心安？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不说话，心有所亏欠是不？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘定要问过明白，在下坦白道这三具尸中，有一人被在下所毙，只这一点我该安葬他同伴三人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "另两人何人所毙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘问这做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要你说就说，啰嗦什么！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不用歇息，再替我挖一个坑。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "哪里还有尸体。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘说笑，在下未死，挖坑做什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姑娘问你不说话，你就要死了，自己不挖谁替你挖！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘不容在下活了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有什么好笑，死到临头，装笑也马虎不过。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "这三名仆人是姑娘的仆人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不管这多，杀人偿命，赶快挖坑吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘三位仆人无一好人，死不足惜，十分抱歉，恕在下不能替他们偿命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不偿命由不得你，告诉你，你死后我没这好心替你安葬，若你认为入土为安，现在赶快挖坑，姑娘成全你助你添上新土。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "多谢了，姑娘要杀请动手吧，只是预告姑娘一声，我会反抗钓。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "萤火之光何足与日月争辉，我要杀你反掌之易。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "若不敌，我自会伸脖子让姑娘宰。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不轻易杀人，你若想活回答我两个问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "好死不如恶活，姑娘问吧，能回答最好免伤和气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "另两人是谁杀的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这三人追的女子何处去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "也不知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "无论对方，有无兵刃，姑娘一战宝剑必定出手。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "在下就这样陪姑娘玩玩。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "姑娘好剑法！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "二姐不可！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊，她来了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "二姐好剑法，若非手下留情，小妹头颅不保。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "四妹，你护这野男子什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "他与我相识，不能见死不救。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮快来见我二姐桃根。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "她……她……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不要多说，见礼呀？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不要见他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "二姐，你与我这位朋友有什么深仇大恨，看在妹妹脸上一切请放过。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "他仅是你的朋友吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "只是朋友二姐不能放过，今天他非死不可，不是我违背门规随便杀人，只因他坏了我的生意，按理该杀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "他坏了二姐什么生意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "生意是你介绍给我的，我已受理买下姚济生的影子，但那条件是撮合他与一位刘姑娘的婚姻，那姑娘被我下了花月妖之毒散失功力已成瓮中之鳖，假以时日定教乖乖下嫁姚济生，可惜不意被她逃走，本可轻易追上却被你这朋友放了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "好啊，原来刘姑娘散失功力是被你下的毒，好个姚济生，卖影子竟是为了求得刘姑娘，她不愿嫁他，怎可采取这种卑劣的手段！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "四妹，你这朋友倒干脆自招了，现在四妹你不能再拦我杀他了吧？听到没有，他还抱怨我下那花月妖呢！刘姑娘敢情是他知心朋友？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公，你当真放了那刘姑娘，你……你为什么放她……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "不为什么，不用说刘姑娘是相识，纵然不识我也不能任你无影门欺负一个女子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "四妹，你自护他，此人不知好歹，无影门在江湖上不惹意外之事，可是有谁妨碍我无影门的行动，死无葬身之地！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "二姐，他是我的影子，你不能杀他！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "原来是妹夫那就例外了，咱们不能一家子闹的啊，四妹，你忒也小气，要独自一人霸占他，怕不分享一杯羹吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_tao_gen",
      "text": "二姐，姚济生的条件你还没办成啊！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gen",
      "speaker_name": "桃根",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "对，我该去办事了，那位姑娘逃到天边我相信也能追她回来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "你别瞎猜，刘姑娘不是我情人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不是你情人，你为何急得这样子，姚济生爱她不惜来卖影子，情不谓不深，你何不让我无影门成全他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "刘姑娘乐意嫁姚济生我不反对，但姚济生用卑劣手段决不行，只要芮玮一口气在，决不让他得逞心意！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "如此说来，你定要阻止二姐的行动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "惟有这样，否则我对不起刘姑娘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你既执拗如此，相公，我要行使我收买影子的权力了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "其实我不愿向你行使权力的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "我影子已卖，不得不听命于你，先天掌已破，心愿得偿，我该履行诺言，可是我能不能再要求你一事？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么事你说，除了阻止二姐行动外，我可以酌情答应。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "我想再求三日宽限，三日后听命姑娘，这三日内都以自由身任意行动。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，你能不能告诉我这三日你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "我要再闯慈悲庵。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你闯慈悲庵我有点不放心，要知我昨晚等你一夜不回，放心不下才赶来看看，若非经过这座森林，你不也是被二姐杀了？你要再去慈悲庵教我如何放心得下呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "生死由命，你要不放心我去冒险，损失了你一条值得利用的性命，那你还来得及收回三日随我自由之情。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我虽女子亦知言出如山，我不劝阻你了，你去吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 81,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    }
